        <mxCell id="2uh8UNP38Qf67Q6y80u1-1" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" value="SYSTEM: Cybersecurity Incident Response Assistant&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;1. Log Ingestion &amp;amp; Parsing&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;1.1 Input Logs&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;- Input: IDS logs or test log files&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;- Process: Read log file, validate input, parse fields&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;- Output: Parsed JSON log entries&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;1.2 Log Validation &amp;amp; Sanitisation&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;- Input: Raw log entries&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;- Process: Validate timestamp, IPs, ports, severity; sanitize strings&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;- Output: Cleaned log entries ready for LLM processing&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;2. LLM Processing&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;2.1 API Key &amp;amp; Model Configuration&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;- Input: User API key, selected model&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;- Process: Store key securely, select API endpoint&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;- Output: Ready configuration for API calls&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;2.2 Incident Summarisation&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;- Input: Parsed JSON log entries&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;- Process: Send to chosen LLM with optional RAG context, include user experience level&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;- Output: Summarised incident description, risk score, mitigation steps&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;3. Data Storage &amp;amp; Authentication&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;3.1 Store Incident Data&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;- Input: Summarised incident data from LLM&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;- Process: Save to Firebase (encrypted, secure)&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;- Output: Persistent incident records&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;3.2 User Authentication&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;- Input: User login credentials&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;- Process: Firebase Auth validation&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;- Output: User session/access token&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;4. Dashboard &amp;amp; Analytics&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;4.1 Analytics Dashboard (Landing Page)&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;- Input: Stored incident data&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;- Process: Aggregate metrics (count, trends, attack types, severity)&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;- Output: Visual analytics charts for users&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;4.2 Incident Log Viewer&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;- Input: Stored incident data&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;- Process: Display incidents, allow filtering and search&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;- Output: Detailed incident tables&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;4.3 Notifications&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;- Input: High-risk incident data&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;- Process: Trigger alerts/notifications&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;- Output: User notifications on dashboard&lt;div&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
